Model

Class Cinema

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Cinema
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Cinema
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class contains all information of a cinema - including its cineplex, whether it is platinum, whether it is 3D cinema, the cinema code and the base price of the cinema.
    Version:
    1.0

        public Cinema(Constant.Cineplex cineplex,
              boolean isPlatinum,
              boolean is3D,
              java.lang.String code,
              double basePrice)
        Allocates a Cinema object and initializes it specified by its cineplex, whether it is boolean, whether it is 3D cinema, the cinema code and the base price of the cinema.
        Parameters:
        cineplex - the cineplex of the cinema
        isPlatinum - true if the cinema is platinum, false if not
        is3D - true if the cinema is a 3D cinema, false if not
        code - the cinema code
        basePrice - the base price of the cinema
